	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I believe that a theme might result in fewer submissions, and the final lineup may feel a bit repetitive if certain elements are present in several games. Both of these issues might hurt the quality of the compilation cartridge. For a cartridge, the more varied the games are, the better.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
